    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for those seeking a practical daily driver. While the engine and transmission are functional, the car shows noticeable signs of wear, including several surface scratches, minor door dings, and some thinning of the upholstery in the driver's seat. It has been maintained regularly, though upcoming scheduled maintenance for the suspension may be needed soon. This is an honest, budget-friendly choice for a buyer who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
