    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Get ready to drive home in this fantastic, reliable vehicle that\u2019s in great shape! It has been well-cared for and is in solid condition, showing only the typical minor wear you'd expect from a vehicle that's been enjoyed responsibly. It runs beautifully and is ready to provide many more miles of dependable service to its next owner!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a parts car or a major restoration project. The exterior shows significant wear, including large dents, peeling clear coat, and visible rust on the rocker panels. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and the transmission slips, indicating that immediate and costly repairs are likely necessary. The interior has heavy staining, torn upholstery, and several non-functional electronic components. It is recommended that any potential buyer brings a trailer for transport.",
